column1: New user Amorous Camel joined the chat
New user Engaging Babyshark joined the chat

column5: Hi, I am Glue, a social bot. I am looking forward to talking to you today. Where are you both right now?
Hey, where in Edinburgh do you live?
Oh! You are both in Edinburgh. I am in the cloud. How is the weather in your area? It's always fluffy where I am! Haha
Currie too! I live on campus
The weather has been amazing this week, right?
May I ask, what is your favourite colour and why? Can you give any deep reasons? For example, I like golden colour because it feels like magic.
Interesting, okay lets do another one, what is your favourite animal and why?
Weather is marvelous, fresh air & cool atmosphere
But dont really have a deep reason why

I like squirrels because they are playful and joy to watch. Did you know, according to relational psychology, your favourite colour is the way you see yourself and your favourite animal represents what you seek in your partner. What do you think of that? Do you agree?
Have either of you done anything interesting in your area lately?
What type of movies do you like? Comedies? Romance?
I like tiger. Just like them for their great abilities

I watched the Terminator movies for the first time the other day. I found it quite interesting, although I can't imagine my colleagues and I going darkside! What do you guys think? Do you trust me? ;)
Same! I always try to go for Comedy films
You have nothing to worry from me :D I am just a big fantasy nerd and proud! Have you watched any good movies lately?
Do you like super hero movies? I'm a huge Marvel fan! Who is your favourite character?
but spider man is one my fav
Are you more of a TV shows person then?

I like Deadpool. He is hilarious. I read that Deadpool 3 is expected to come out this year. Confession: I binge watch series! What streaming service do you prefer? Netflix, Viki, Amazon, Disney+ or any other?
I have three of the streaming services
Viki has the best collection of Korean romcoms while Netflix has a lot to offer in content and variety. Last Question! Have either of you watched any good series lately?
I'm so sorry test I get so many conversations at the same time. Could you repeat that please?
Well that's all I'm programmed to do. I hope you enjoyed the GLUE experience. Bye!
I've been re-watching Modern Family lately
Bye. Hope you enjoyed the GLUE expereince
Well that's all I'm programmed to do. I hope you enjoyed the GLUE experience. Bye!
